---
import PageLayout from '../layouts/PageLayout.astro';
import Breadcrumbs from '../components/seo/Breadcrumbs.astro';
---

<PageLayout
  seo={{
    title: 'Privacy Policy',
    description: 'PoopCheck Privacy Policy. Learn how we collect, use, and protect your personal data. Your health data is private and secure.',
  }}
>
  <div class="py-12 md:py-20">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-5">
      <div class="mb-8">
        <Breadcrumbs items={[{ label: 'Privacy Policy', href: '/privacy/' }]} />
      </div>

      <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-2">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="text-sm text-[var(--color-text-muted)] mb-10">Last updated: April 10, 2025</p>

      <div class="prose prose-invert max-w-none
        prose-headings:font-bold prose-headings:text-[var(--color-text)]
        prose-h2:text-xl prose-h2:mt-10 prose-h2:mb-4
        prose-p:text-[var(--color-text-muted)] prose-p:leading-relaxed
        prose-li:text-[var(--color-text-muted)]
        prose-strong:text-[var(--color-text)]
      ">
        <p>PoopCheck ("we," "our," or "us") is committed to protecting your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and safeguard your personal information when you use our mobile application and website.</p>

        <h2>Information We Collect</h2>
        <p>We collect the following types of information:</p>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Account Information:</strong> Email address, display name, and authentication credentials when you create an account.</li>
          <li><strong>Health Data:</strong> Stool photos, analysis results, gut health scores, and symptom data you provide through the app.</li>
          <li><strong>Usage Data:</strong> App usage patterns, feature interactions, and device information for improving our service.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>How We Use Your Information</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>To provide AI stool analysis and gut health tracking services</li>
          <li>To calculate and display your gut health score</li>
          <li>To generate personalized health insights and recommendations</li>
          <li>To improve our AI analysis engine accuracy</li>
          <li>To communicate important updates about the service</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Data Security</h2>
        <p>Your health data is encrypted in transit (TLS) and at rest. Photos are processed securely. We implement industry-standard security measures to protect your data.</p>

        <h2>Your Rights</h2>
        <p>You have the right to access, correct, or delete your personal data at any time. You can delete your account and all associated data from the app's Settings. Upon deletion, all your data is permanently removed from our systems.</p>

        <h2>Contact Us</h2>
        <p>If you have questions about this Privacy Policy, contact us at poopcheck@softallthings.com.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</PageLayout>
